{"tid":1619042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想係連登熄燈之前 同大家講句！加油！","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:28:38.000Z","uid":250356,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9e13c753c640b565468856eba1a7ab04aadd282a","tid":1619042,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"大大話話大家都努力咗四個月，有手足被補、中咗催淚彈皮膚敏感、有手足被射眼、有手足差啲被謀殺後重要比人控告！甚至有手足被殺&hellip;死因不明！我哋甘心咁咩？<br />\n<br />\n我哋踏出咗第一步，就算含著淚都要行到最後一步！就算輸都要輸得甘心命抵，我哋對唔對得重上面講嘅手足，我哋回想返六月嘅時候！點解我哋要出嚟？就係為咗對抗/推翻，呢個極權政府、獨裁政府！<br />\n<br />\n想同大家講：大家就算失望，也不能絕望，我哋每一個人都係好微小，對抗政府甚至係以卵擊石，但其實我哋一啲都唔細小，只要我哋七百萬人一齊向政府對抗，只要踏出第一步，就有成功嘅可能性，唔好放棄，香港人加油。<br />\n<br />\n我想約定你哋，煲底，真係除下面罩攬住！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相認！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n香港人！！反抗！！！！"},{"pid":"981744204ac62b9061dff19cb4e52a9e5638f4c6","tid":1619042,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"大家加油<br />\n今日要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ada01d50b6088f5d564af928a3a716d00bc2af","tid":1619042,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981744204ac62b9061dff19cb4e52a9e5638f4c6","tid":1619042,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"大家加油<br />\n今日要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"真係小心啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔想放負，想比多啲正能量大家！！！<br />\n<br />\n香港人！反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要睇情況啊"},{"pid":"bac45a05529924a70c4b4ea4eb727bc9ac96460b","tid":1619042,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a63845c7d170e6185afa95fc1c520a4e840986","tid":1619042,"uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"我知道，我哋出去可能會好危險，但係！我哋更加！更加！唔應該沉默，我哋嘅地方，唔應該係政府決定，甚至係中共，呢道係我嘅家！只有民選嘅政府，先可以代表香港人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb55f0eec36a03e2e2c43950377adda99d53d7f","tid":1619042,"uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"香港人！反抗！"},{"pid":"8262dafd2185736559614eb9e0827d38909b6de9","tid":1619042,"uid":11447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"各位同行兒女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一生平安"},{"pid":"d7c2385d5fe1857d57c4f10c960a76f86de178dd","tid":1619042,"uid":314633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125bbfe15df9130302c2fc5a561374fefe6ef3be","tid":1619042,"uid":106478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"大家加油 煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80365c8c910f6d788102b84a3f46e4f644c4b568","tid":1619042,"uid":321024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475f9cfc16a0c1d3740b87bb695565510d86e83a","tid":1619042,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"125bbfe1